{"tid":1292534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉發高登］18區社運入一入黎，記述6/7號晚油塘B出口所發生的街站前後經過","createTime":"2019-07-07T11:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T11:37:46.000Z","uid":41602,"like":124,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a98db7675dd62bcd0a0fd8727f665c253d56ed07","tid":1292534,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:10:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<strong>大家好，本文謹代表某些油塘街坊立場，<br />\n經過多人論證還原事件，<br />\n如有錯漏，歡迎補充及指正。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>事緣網傳油塘區會在7月6號晚上十一點在油塘站B出口麥當勞對出空地有街站活動。<br />\n而宣傳清楚寫明：<span style=\"color: gold;\">打氣活動及贈飲</span><br />\n當晚不談政治沒有政黨沒有外國勢力！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLrOGQU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLrOGQU.png&h=5f6a7fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">據消息人士透露，藍絲公務員及紀律部隊瘋傳一些謠言</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">指今晚油塘會有暴徒搞事。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">如此低劣的抹黑行為，實在令油塘街坊非常失望</span></span><br />\n<ins>注：油塘有幾座紀律部隊宿舍（五千人左右）<br />\n以下為消息人士所據供對話截圖</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKT5JVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKT5JVk.png&h=b1a134c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiV4e10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiV4e10.png&h=437293b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>10:30-11:00 </strong></span><br />\n當一眾油塘巴絲集合準備開始時，已察覺周圍不友善的眼光及人士圍觀，氣氛一度緊張。<br />\n及後據消息人士透露，多數是油塘各類乜乜樓乜乜苑乜乜委員會成員。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>11:00 - 11:55</strong></span> <br />\n活動開始一個鐘內，已經聚集了不少油塘之友，派發寫滿愛心打氣字句的水杯，有街坊自發提供各類飲品及小食。<br />\n而張貼的標語只是<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">*加油站*及*油塘樹窿*</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5RvaK5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5RvaK5.png&h=9888a590&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h2A7XpO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh2A7XpO.png&h=f0c80595&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NRXeCpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNRXeCpP.png&h=002b06b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNQWQKQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNQWQKQ.png&h=6442a1c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeAzCfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeAzCfF.png&h=31cc4ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">開站不久，人流開始聚集，油塘人有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYOEOw1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYOEOw1.png&h=4bc4974a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oejQaLn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoejQaLn.png&h=5901450d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><div style=\"text-align: left;\">期間亦有油麗商場保安前來，表示接收投訴，希望街站盡快撒走。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（在此先和當晚保安及貴公司道歉，要你地頂一頂壓力，謝謝理解及協助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n而至於為何在接到所謂大量擾民或嘈音投訴，在場警方沒有展開行動？既然警方認為事態不需要他們出面干預，亦表示當晚情況並非投訴人士所講般惡劣。<br />\n（在此感謝警方理解，嗱.....當晚警方真係俾足面我地，佢地認為無事發生好和平到最後清場都無干涉架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</div></ins><br />\n<br />\n願意留低的人士各站一旁，大家十分和平，當中只有零星人士經過破口大罵或惡意影年輕人大頭相，但大家相當克制忍讓。<br />\n<ins>注：如此一個加油站都被人無理取鬧，同周柏豪叫人登記做選民但被罵港獨，有何分別？咁成個政府搞選舉又係咪港獨？<br />\n如此邏輯下，年輕人出黎搞正面活動都要被排斥的話，我地點相信政府有心同年輕人溝通！</ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7czAmQb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7czAmQb.png&h=5f4436ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而當晚緊張到一副不滿暴徒搞事的只有那幾位乜乜委員乜乜主席（反正我唔撚識你地乜水啦），整晚俾說話俾面識大家聽。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以下收錄他們奇趣對話</span><br />\n：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你地200萬人遊行又點呀？代表仲有400萬人支持政府呀！</span></span><br />\n：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你知唔知今晚你地衰咩？就係衰乜都無搞呀！</span></span><br />\n我嘗試去理解，但唔明，以下開放俾連登仔理解。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>注1：董建華講得無錯，通識科太失敗，導致年輕人無腦思考。<br />\n注2：勞工及福利局長羅致光說明60歲才是年輕人<br />\n<br />\n你班<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">60歲年輕人</span></strong>唔該試下用腦fact check果啲所謂瘋傳短訊啦，睇少啲ccTVB愚民政策。</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>12:00</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">還原基本步</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UtOYjFt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtOYjFt.png&h=f395b55a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實當晚年輕人已經做了一個最佳例子，開放一個平台讓大家去接觸了解我們在想什麼干甚麼，但為什麼當區建制陣營人士如臨大敵，選擇站在旁邊，一副食鹽多過你班廢青食米既心態，只會嘴臉上挑釁大家。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">常言道社區是社會的縮影，你們這樣的心態跟林鄭政府的敵視態度以及專橫有何分別？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果重新來過，你們可以嘗試行過黎，拎杯野，同年輕人傾計嗎？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當然我絕對相信大家會有下一次機會</span>，未必係油塘區，18區區皆可，大門永遠打開。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: right;\">嗚謝：高登、香港討論區、Bb王國</div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>屌你老母你班連登仔一世都搞唔到咁高汁既活動</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;"},{"pid":"a9b0cf26a8830df539ed0edd00a512782fdb3a39","tid":1292534,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"414eb88484580d78c6f006f146ad28bdbde75fd5","tid":1292534,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9b0cf26a8830df539ed0edd00a512782fdb3a39","tid":1292534,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"第一個回覆很重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我無野講</strong>"},{"pid":"9ac8748f425117b07dfc4f666d0248ee7ae75cd7","tid":1292534,"uid":39494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"你知唔知今晚你地衰咩？就係衰乜都無搞呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ff91fff0bb2899afa3f4d45c973970cc2c8874","tid":1292534,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"928a09c7b8218a6123aad28c4f347d64746c0663","tid":1292534,"uid":262825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:36:27.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98eb2b0eb2e3d84b0260f525e641f8324de6ca93","tid":1292534,"uid":41602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ac8748f425117b07dfc4f666d0248ee7ae75cd7","tid":1292534,"uid":39494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"你知唔知今晚你地衰咩？就係衰乜都無搞呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"啲廢老講野係咁on9，<br />\n可能佢真心等暴徒搞事，佢就可以大展拳腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d880b46249b76cb914e18cbd57e977097984e641","tid":1292534,"uid":48188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"<code>推推推推 我無野講 我要副本 我搵律師 我唔會簽 我要毛氈 我要飲食 我唔解鎖 唔好凶我 我投訴你</code>"},{"pid":"b3544649b407688761839529102b85f874ba5ca7","tid":1292534,"uid":87820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:44:50.000Z","msg":"我住油塘。 琴晚唔知有咁既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558ee1e81a4ac320ee5a287be7f3fac62728f6db","tid":1292534,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:49:57.000Z","msg":"<code>我冇嘢講</code>"},{"pid":"1387fac69d96f51054d12292c572e199ee8dd130","tid":1292534,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"最後個句做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，依家要鬥高汁啊?"},{"pid":"f6dbedb1d2ca5c617e14865122c818ae66870089","tid":1292534,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:26:00.000Z","msg":"一邊話社會充斥負面，一屌加油站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353a10df89df0bdabc79621ff47f5d855d208eba","tid":1292534,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五大訴求濃縮版，往後示威請大家一齊嗌五大口號：<br />\n<br />\n1.）撤回逃犯修例<br />\n2.）撤回暴動定性<br />\n3.）釋放被捕示威者<br />\n4.）追究警方暴力濫權<br />\n5.）我要雙普選</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9347e0aa8b1dccc53bb0f49965f55a2cf92f79fe"